https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/425TJYJHcJv5ppNG2wMxIgxLfEe.jpg Coral Reef Adventure follows the real-life expedition of ocean explorers and underwater filmmakers Howard and Michele Hall. Using large-format cameras, the Halls guide us to the islands and sun-drenched waters of the South Pacific to document the health and beauty of coral reefs.
